                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8615" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0084</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3042 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“擀”为人先出劲道——杂八得面皮书写规模经济风云</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dare to Take the Lead&#160; ——ZABADE Rolling Cold Noddle Writes the Process of Economies of Scale</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王颖晖，齐悦童，张晔，孙瑄，余凤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西杂八得食品有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">5 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模经济；长期平均成本；范围经济；生产决策；2024百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Economies of scale, Long-term average cost, Economies of scope, Production decisions</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从小麦到面皮，从田间到车间，从餐馆到直播间，从宝鸡到海外，传统非遗小吃的生产模式变革书写着乡村振兴致富产业链上一张擀面皮的规模化、品牌化、集聚化发展历程，而只有将产能扩大与市场需求匹配，将生产规划置于长期生产决策的考虑中，管理者才能驱动规模经济效应与企业绩效正向循环。案例通过描述陕西宝鸡杂八得食品公司不断扩大产能、提高生产规模，由一家小作坊发展成龙头企业的发展历程，进而提出下一步关于公司产品发展方向的生产决策问题。案例旨在帮助学生掌握规模经济、范围经济、长期平均成本、生产函数等相关理论与方法，启发学生展开对经济学理论如何融入具体经营管理行为的深度思考，提高学生在产业高速发展、竞争压力剧增的供给侧改革宏观环境下提高管理决策的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">From wheat to dough, from the field to the workshop, from the restaurant to the live broadcast room, from Baoji city to overseas, the transformation of the production mode of traditional intangible cultural heritage snacks writes the development process of scale, branding and agglomeration of  rolling cold noddles in the industrial chain of rural revitalization and prosperity. Only by matching capacity expansion to market demand and placing production planning in the context of long-term production decisions can managers drive a positive cycle of economies of scale and business performance. The case describes the development process of Shaanxi Baoji ZABADE Food Co., Ltd. from a small workshop to a leading enterprise by continuously expanding production capacity and increasing production scale, and then puts forward the next production decision-making question on the company&#39;s product development direction. The case aims to help students master the theories and methods related to economies of scale, economies of scope, long-term average cost, and production function, inspire students to develop in-depth thinking about how economic theories can be integrated into specific business management behaviors, and improve students&#39; ability to improve management decision-making in the macro environment of supply-side reform with rapid industrial development and increasing competitive pressure.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理经济学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模经济；长期平均成本；生产函数；范围经济</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
